almost a year since this 💍 this is for those who wonder if they will ever find their person.. I swear all of it—the heartbreak, bad dates, ghosting, or whatever it is—are worth it because *the* one is worth the wait. met my now fiancé in my late 20s (on @hinge might I add!) then covid happened… so it took us almost half a decade to get to this moment lol but still!! wouldn’t have changed anything about it 🥹
.

lol it was a little stressful filming these with him being a couple of feet infront of me but I knew this was going to be the trip that it will happen! There were so many signs… (we also went ring shopping a couple of months ago!) but the biggest giveaway was that he told me days before we left that he made dinner reservations for the 2nd night which he never does. 🙈 (PS I plan all our trips 😅) apparently, he’s been in touch with the staff at @amanyara_resort since we booked this trip - finding the florist, photographer, even the perfect spot in the resort! We’re both so happy with how it all turned out 🥹 many thanks to them for making sure everything went smoothly. 🤍 
.
